subject: Baseball
lead_paragraph: Jeff Francoeur hit a game-ending, two-run homer against Chad Qualls in the ninth inning, and the Atlanta Braves overcame a 10-strikeout performance by Randy Johnson to beat the visiting Arizona Diamondbacks, 3-1.
